FEEDBACK LIFECYCLE

@startuml
title Path Status & Feedback Merging (State Machine)

[*] --> Unknown : No feedback available

state Unknown {
}
Unknown --> Optimal : Recent majority positive feedbacks
Unknown --> Warning : Mixed feedbacks OR insufficient consensus
Unknown --> RequiresMaintenance : Recent majority negative feedbacks

state Optimal {
}
Optimal --> Warning : Mixed feedbacks OR insufficient recent positives
Optimal --> RequiresMaintenance : Recent majority negative feedbacks

state Warning {
}
Warning --> Optimal : Recent majority positive feedbacks
Warning --> RequiresMaintenance : Recent majority negative feedbacks

state RequiresMaintenance {
}
RequiresMaintenance --> Warning : mixed feedbacks OR old negative data
RequiresMaintenance --> Optimal : Recent several positive feedbacks

@enduml